Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本字幕由喵萌奶茶屋製作 僅供交流試看之用 請勿用於商業用途\N\N翻譯：Nemeton　後期：MIR　繁化：錯黨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:05.46,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,德勒韋斯大人怎麼會在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.14,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,一會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.89,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,火焰風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:14.35,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我來開路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.06,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.05,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,好 長勢不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.85,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們開始下一個階段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.87,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用這片地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:14.45,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 領主大人已經同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:16.28,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:16.92,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.13,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個就是聖女之術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.55,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.79,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個就是聖女之術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.15,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經可以自由使用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:43.19,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳為什麼要在這種地方使用…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.89,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是為什麼不在我面前使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.15,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,欺負我嗎？還是說故意使壞？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:49.95,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:54.25,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是我想要練習一下魔法 所以她帶我來了這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.17,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:03:00.67,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊才剛剛準備好 還什麼都沒有種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:04.30,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖女之術也不會對田地有危害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.61,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:11.83,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不過雖說沒有危害 可對土地說不定有影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:12.45,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.61,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,能感覺到奇特的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.24,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,能判斷出有什麼樣的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:21.77,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:24.63,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,要麼魔力會滯留在土地中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:27.98,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,要麼就是礦物會被附魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.23,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,兩種情況都有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:33.49,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也就是假設階段而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.00,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,要仔細驗證一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.24,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.66,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩人聊得怪開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.96,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們開始下一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:45.94,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:47.52,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.95,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:55.97,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:57.17,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.36,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:12.16,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,看來聖女之術會消耗大量的魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.69,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.88,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.82,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是讓我連續用了好幾次…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.94,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,反覆練習才能掌握好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:28.40,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,以後還得多加練習 提升發動魔法的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.38,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？還…還要更快嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.79,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是有點…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:38.04,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,發動魔法之前我需要不少準備的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.52,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.86,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來發動的條件是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:46.78,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.13,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.02,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不好說出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.11,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.04,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這就算了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.11,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳願意說出來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:01.06,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:04.21,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:07.62,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.12,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.67,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了 我聽說你在這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.44,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意 你有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.10,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,討伐隊伍重新編排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.80,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.08,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖也一起確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.70,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:29.08,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.28,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,史萊姆嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:34.56,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,有點等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.10,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖小姐 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.11,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,愛良 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.35,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我們好像是一隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:58.05,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 愛良也要參與進攻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.91,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,估計是要看情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.42,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我基本上是負責治療
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:07.40,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,因為前輩說團長大概不會參與治療
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.12,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.89,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 聖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.32,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.69,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.29,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,萊昂先生也和我們一隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:21.00,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.68,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 聖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.48,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖大人 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.13,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.70,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是灰燼惡魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:31.51,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.14,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,某次大規模討伐任務中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.81,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,他將怪物連同周圍的一切都燃燒殆盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:39.93,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就有了這麼個外號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:43.49,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能控制住自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:44.72,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.35,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,希望這次任務的森林沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:50.73,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.82,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,得提前拜託他別引燃森林…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.07,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,冰矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.66,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,範圍守護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.01,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.59,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,治療
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.28,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:24.10,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.93,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖女大人 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.43,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.69,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,怪物的數量增多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:33.39,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,史萊姆的數量也變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.38,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定離那沼澤不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:37.93,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,德勒韋斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.71,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 愛護森林是吧 我沒忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.35,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,怪物出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.38,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,迎敵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.25,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.43,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,保持警戒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.56,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.16,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,保持陣型！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.25,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:28.89,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,水牆！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.22,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,冰箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.24,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,冰牆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.21,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,地刺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:48.64,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,治療
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:50.70,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:53.41,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.23,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.91,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是時候 火矛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.26,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.07,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 聖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.33,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.47,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,治療
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:22.66,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.73,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:27.72,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.93,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,只是聖女之術消耗的魔力過多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.44,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,在找到沼澤之前希望妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:44.92,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.95,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖大人 從這個位置可以淨化到黑色沼澤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.92,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,能…能不能靠近一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.96,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:26.59,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣我們現在也無法撤退 只有前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.71,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,準備上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:39.99,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.05,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,全員衝鋒！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.14,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,電團
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.20,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.50,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:03.93,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.18,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.30,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,團長！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.44,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:33.31,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來對付史萊姆 聖大人專注發動魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.04,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.13,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.04,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,業火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.49,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖大人 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.43,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,火矛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.69,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊時間 必須抓緊時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:44.37,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.26,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 只是在發呆…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:53.23,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 今天很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.98,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也累了吧 早些休息比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.33,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝團長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:05.88,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.50,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那我就先休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.49,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我送妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.31,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.46,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.88,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.64,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意 那妳好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.78,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.16,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.05,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是不是有什麼心事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:59.77,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 再要求更多就有些任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:05.73,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我還是無法就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:13.53,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖 我是王國的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.87,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍就是王的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.34,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,可如果可能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.39,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望成為守護妳的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:28.15,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,能否讓我實現妳的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.67,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:24.67,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 那什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.12,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,要專心 專心…專心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:33.62,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.93,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:39.85,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不是…你一直盯著我 我不好集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.76,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 妳請便 不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.19,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以做到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.29,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.31,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.36,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,願森林恢復生機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.04,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:18.46,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.17,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…克勞斯納的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.27,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖？聖！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.45,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:45.95,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.46,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.39,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 妳醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.77,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:05.52,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是累壞了吧 突然就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:09.55,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我真的沒事了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.59,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳讓我們擔心的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:26.32,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:34.49,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,我想自己走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:37.58,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.93,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,那至少能讓我陪伴著妳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:00.74,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.90,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙妳照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:16.60,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我才是得到了不少幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.89,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不在了 藥水製作又不容易了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.54,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不至於…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:27.71,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不至於 只有妳能製作那麼多藥水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:34.21,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不過正如領主大人所說 妳就是我們的希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.17,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.76,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,喲！準備回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:38.77,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.27,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.17,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,萊昂先生也多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:46.18,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 王都待煩了隨時可以來這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:51.12,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 交給你還不如讓她來我這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:53.16,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖 該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:54.32,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:57.22,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們的幫助和照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.65,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎再來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:07.70,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖女的魔力還真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.19,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連森林都再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.73,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:15.27,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不過她的厲害之處不只是魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.38,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們都擁有那樣的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:22.72,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？老太妳一把年紀 人傻了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:24.07,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.78,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼複雜的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.72,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖女的魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.22,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,就是愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:09.12,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,還是自己家最舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:16.58,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,過不了多久又會有新的討伐任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:19.21,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,又要麻煩聖了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:20.84,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:22.23,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.30,0:23:26.55,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 霍克大人不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:29.51,Dial-CHT,,0000,0000,0000,,聖女的魔力…
